{"tid":1825863,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"連登過山車膠討論區","createTime":"2020-01-15T16:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T06:38:35.000Z","uid":256077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cc81da42b733ace0ca92f1085ecd6683392a2f","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"呢排鄰國武漢肺炎都殺到來<br />\n竟然呢個垃圾港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲擔心緊啲樂園有無人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係科水俾啲醫院或者起多幾間醫院<br />\n或者俾啲大學做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係用成106億俾個樂園起設施<br />\n仲誇過十幾億既垃圾行人天橋<br />\n係佢既10倍有多<br />\n而且呢106億仲要俾個過撚哂氣既海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話俾迪士尼都話順氣啲始終係國際品牌<br />\n(雖然都係好撚唔順氣）<br />\n<br />\n海狗公園拆撚咗個海洋劇場<br />\n諗住攞錢起多啲機動遊戲<br />\n作為一個玩開Planet Coaster 既過山車膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住100幾億應該起咗好多正野<br />\n包括啲比較特別既過山車<br />\n結果睇吓佢個概念圖<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全部都係過撚哂氣或者垃圾既過山車<br />\n完全冇吸引性可言<br />\n（詳細可以睇下面個Post）<br />\n<br />\n我見到啲狗官係政府個發佈會到講到幾撚柒正咁<br />\n仲要話訪問5個國家既人話佢地想要互動既野<br />\n根本係搵藉口起啲垃圾平野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要講啲專業既terms （例如 Dive Coaster)<br />\n搏人哋唔知道係乜9嘢來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且唔同飛機巴士地鐵<br />\n你一搞啲垃圾即刻會有飛機膠巴膠鐵膠屌<br />\n假如某日因航話要買C919或者A330咁<br />\n啲飛機膠一定第一個屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係因為亞洲相比歐美係少好多<br />\n所謂Coaster Enthusiasts（過山車膠）<br />\n所以可能會比較少啲人屌啲樂園起乜<br />\n<br />\n所以今日特登開呢個Post<br />\n係可以解答下大家對過山車既問題<br />\n例如啲好Pro 既terms<br />\n (海狗公園整出來搏你地唔識）<br />\n例如 Dive Coaster, Launch Coaster, Spike Coaster<br />\n同埋我第一次開下面個Post 之後<br />\n下面有巴打話想小弟講多啲關於過山車既嘢<br />\n<br />\n其實宜家啲新聞係介紹過山車果緊成日誤導人<br />\n例如Baby Condom同香導啲藍屍好撚鍾意去既<br />\n        鄰國長隆海洋王國入面果部 Parrot Coaster<br />\n        啲新聞話佢係世界最長既過山車<br />\n 其實應該係世界最長既寛翼式過山車<br />\n 係差好撚遠<br />\n 真正最長既過山車係喺日本<br />\n 結果都成功呃到一批人<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩關於過山車既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他遊樂設施都ok<br />\n或者去過咩樂園好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者想屌柒個垃圾港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可以Post上來<br />\n小弟不材，盡量解答下大家<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都關注下呢100億喺駛咗係邊<br />\n因為呢個數係垃圾行人天橋既10倍<br />\n絕對唔係少數<br />\n大家已經都好努力為左擱置呢條天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家玩完沙中線三跑行人天橋明日大愚<br />\n又想玩多樣大白象工程<br />\n最慘係海狗公園連水上樂園未起到<br />\n又問政府攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41b498ac2a9230e8ee1a622fd52a941f48a6de9","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"睇下海馬公園用106億起啲乜嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1823946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1823946</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22cc61d4e63f2337a9e4a30156e6793b387d71b0","tid":1825863,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:03:17.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4325e7aff1fb0f40485c8fb141a861fc4f88fc6","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec65a89bcbe696365bbf279c7f07206217c6eb1","tid":1825863,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"點睇韓國嗰個唔知乜樂園 木製過山車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a51a4848a79cf495b31c568c73c24bac8064d9","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dec65a89bcbe696365bbf279c7f07206217c6eb1","tid":1825863,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"點睇韓國嗰個唔知乜樂園 木製過山車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"你話Everland部T Express?<br />\n<br />\n果部好嘢嚟<br />\n係瑞士名牌Intamin做<br />\n佢雖然係木製過山車但係唔同一般木製咁<br />\n聽人講坐得好似鋼製咁順唔Chok<br />\n但係佢之前個最斜紀錄好似13年一早比人破左"},{"pid":"2f8e7649552584bcd8a02116f75e7daf30a4b5f0","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4513426e709576715e12d2ded64c533c244951fd","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b90fb1a4b7c0a81a3302bf6a8d10a131488e33f","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d955e6cce7d709edb204908a77bc07845b242230","tid":1825863,"uid":47041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"鍾意玩過山車<br />\n但身邊無乜人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc80e7a8b6211df420148608257c860db73e9c31","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d955e6cce7d709edb204908a77bc07845b242230","tid":1825863,"uid":47041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"鍾意玩過山車<br />\n但身邊無乜人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇今次海狗公園攞成百億起嘢？"},{"pid":"16f4178d05fb7b94f71cd17794bf04773e5e6e28","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36399c04b23ab870e47756a3f739bb489e0d0b16","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519380480e77ee6d23da05f828ecdae9c845eaae","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a84f3a1e882b8d76be0b4282fef2f73454b1f4f","tid":1825863,"uid":63127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"有時見啲過山車望落好牙煙<br />\n有冇咩地方既過山車/款你係覺得唔好搵條命去較飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149d85f342890ae3a09809ffc7cd16bf69fffd27","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a84f3a1e882b8d76be0b4282fef2f73454b1f4f","tid":1825863,"uid":63127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"有時見啲過山車望落好牙煙<br />\n有冇咩地方既過山車/款你係覺得唔好搵條命去較飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"鄰國製果啲<br />\n乜7金馬中治果啲<br />\n唔好攞命搏<br />\n但係鄰國有啲樂園<br />\n都完全唔會買鄰國貨（例如長隆咁）<br />\n嘉年華或者臨時起果啲過山車會比較危險<br />\n大型樂園果啲會比較安全"},{"pid":"224dae4a61626eb124871c6abe4b4a4af5d2ea0b","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人知道港共政權幾無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d897560d2a77b41aa0192f57c716421b5406979d","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb16fce135cc67865b080ea1e865680e9ea0cd","tid":1825863,"uid":1049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"過山車都有專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ed97fbca4bf2dbc9d5a178e1c7e56f25210df2","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26fb16fce135cc67865b080ea1e865680e9ea0cd","tid":1825863,"uid":1049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"過山車都有專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"歐美有好撚多Coaster Enthusiasts <br />\n佢哋同香港啲鐵膠一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一有新過山車開幕果日<br />\n就即刻一朝早係樂園門口等<br />\n樂園一開幕就即刻衝入去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57e10f6dac391d2642c8361333f4aa739f129f7","tid":1825863,"uid":133687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇香港啲過山車 算唔算高質 同埋安全性嚟講係咪算ok<br />\n我之前去過six flags玩 感覺係正啲 但係唔知點解覺得唔係好安全 好似好求奇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5171a133e438fb8b54142a6d6738a892492c03e8","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a57e10f6dac391d2642c8361333f4aa739f129f7","tid":1825863,"uid":133687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇香港啲過山車 算唔算高質 同埋安全性嚟講係咪算ok<br />\n我之前去過six flags玩 感覺係正啲 但係唔知點解覺得唔係好安全 好似好求奇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"香港啲過山車全部都好嘢來<br />\n算係名牌貨<br />\n最緊要唔係買支貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果刺唔刺激係睇個Layout design多個個款<br />\nSix Flags既話因為佢哋實在有太撚多過山車<br />\n有啲名牌貴野有啲cheap野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家Six Flags 唔同90-00年代果陣咁輝煌<br />\n一早已經江河日下摺柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cb05b1b82c13a4e61b43d2ce7ae6b2e939f07f","tid":1825863,"uid":301291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"dual spike coaster (光速追逐）外國都算少見 <br />\n睇concept art 應該同呢個差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"https://rcdb.com/15717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frcdb.com%2F15717.htm&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=7de1cec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rcdb.com/15717.htm</a><br />\n獨特性同可玩性嚟講都算高嘅<br />\n<br />\nlaunch coaster （小徑飛車）有啲期待<br />\n唔知邊間廠<br />\n睇concept art seat configuration係6x2x2 24人<br />\n用over the shoulder restraint<br />\n<br />\ndive coaster (深海狂潛)<br />\nb&amp;m 大廠做<br />\n睇concept art seat configuration 8x3 24人<br />\n睇高度同seat configuration應該係幾十年前超短個啲layout<br />\n而家新個啲dive coaster多數seat configuration係6x3 18人<br />\n<br />\n其他過山車都係鳩鳩地就唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n寧願佢慳番啲錢起rmc ibox/b&amp;m giga算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d051ac79c023d7bdd6907d500931840c9f429035","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70cb05b1b82c13a4e61b43d2ce7ae6b2e939f07f","tid":1825863,"uid":301291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"dual spike coaster (光速追逐）外國都算少見 <br />\n睇concept art 應該同呢個差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"https://rcdb.com/15717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frcdb.com%2F15717.htm&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=7de1cec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rcdb.com/15717.htm</a><br />\n獨特性同可玩性嚟講都算高嘅<br />\n<br />\nlaunch coaster （小徑飛車）有啲期待<br />\n唔知邊間廠<br />\n睇concept art seat configuration係6x2x2 24人<br />\n用over the shoulder restraint<br />\n<br />\ndive coaster (深海狂潛)<br />\nb&amp;m 大廠做<br />\n睇concept art seat configuration 8x3 24人<br />\n睇高度同seat configuration應該係幾十年前超短個啲layout<br />\n而家新個啲dive coaster多數seat configuration係6x3 18人<br />\n<br />\n其他過山車都係鳩鳩地就唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n寧願佢慳番啲錢起rmc ibox/b&amp;m giga算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"我之前有Post講Spike Coaster<br />\n垃圾到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCoasterforce個個都負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲屌點解意大利貪平買<br />\n買部 Vekoma Motorbike 好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小俓飛車我估係B&amp;M Surf Coaster<br />\nSurf Coaster係B&amp;M新出款<br />\n我之前Post都有講<br />\n但係睇個Layout好似麻麻地<br />\n<br />\nDive Coaster 我估佢會用1排8-10位果款<br />\n屌你Dive Coaster已經起到濫唒仲起<br />\n屌你港共政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實剩買一部特別少少既都夠做<br />\n例如giga hyper mega<br />\n或者你講 rmc ibox <br />\n但係我覺得地理位置會有少少難做<br />\n<br />\n反而我覺得最適合係<br />\nMack Xtreme Spinning<br />\nLaunch + inversion 果款<br />\n始終成個亞洲都冇<br />\n海狗公園又買過 Mack<br />\n而且就算Sliver Dollar City 啲地型<br />\n都可以整得好刺激<br />\n仲要部野轉下轉下咁款<br />\n一定唔引好多非過山車膠來玩"},{"pid":"c37f386ce43fd544471ff4c30797360cf9fbb76c","tid":1825863,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:57:15.000Z"